    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it's been such a reliable partner on the road. It's in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, worry-free ride that still looks fantastic in the driveway. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to shout if you have any questions at all!",
